claims.sentence:
Initial follow-up SAQ nonrespondents were sent email reminders followed by WhatsApp/Telegram messages and phone calls to minimize loss to follow-up.Randomization
In all, n=65,880 students were invited from the general student body and n=678 from clinic waiting lists (Figure 1).
These students were randomized with equal allocation across the 3 intervention arms (Figure 1).

Interventions
Figure 1.

Figure 1 shows the breakdown of the students invited to participate who did versus did not complete the SAQs, the breakdown of exclusion criteria for those who completed the SAQ but were not randomized, the distribution of follow-up SAQ completion among those randomized by arm, and the distribution of starting and completing 3+ hours online among those who completed the SAQ and were assigned to the i-CBT arms.
